---

<BaseLayout
  title="Mochila de emergencia: ¿Qué tamaño? Guía y contenido"
  description="Guía completa de mochilas para tu kit 72 horas: tipos, capacidades, cómo cargar correctamente y qué incluir."
  locale="es"
  dateModified="2025-12-15"
  schemaType="Article"
>
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <nav class="text-sm mb-4">
          <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[--color-text-muted]">
            <li><a href="/es/" class="hover:text-[--color-accent-primary]">Inicio</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li><a href="/es/componentes/" class="hover:text-[--color-accent-primary]">Componentes</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-[--color-text-primary]">Mochilas</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        <h1 class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <Icon name="Backpack" size={32} class="text-[--color-accent-primary]" />
          Mochilas de Emergencia
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-[--color-text-secondary]">
          La mochila es el contenedor de todo tu kit de supervivencia. Elegir la correcta
          y saber cargarla bien puede marcar la diferencia entre evacuación cómoda o agotadora.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Recommendation -->
      <div class="card p-6 mb-8 border-l-4 border-l-[--color-accent-primary]">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2 text-[--color-text-primary] flex items-center gap-2">
          <Icon name="Backpack" size={20} class="text-[--color-accent-primary]" />
          Recomendación rápida
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[--color-text-secondary] m-0">
          <strong>Capacidad ideal:</strong> 35-45L por adulto para kit 72h completo.
          <strong>Clave:</strong> Cinturón lumbar + funda impermeable.
          <strong>Presupuesto:</strong> 50-100€ para una mochila de calidad.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Weight Warning -->
      <div class="p-4 bg-[--color-status-warning]/10 border border-[--color-status-warning]/30 rounded-lg mb-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-[--color-text-secondary] m-0 flex items-start gap-2">
          <Icon name="AlertTriangle" size={18} class="text-[--color-status-warning] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
          <span><strong class="text-[--color-status-warning]">Regla del peso:</strong> No cargues más del
          <strong>15% de tu peso corporal</strong> si no estás en forma, o 20% máximo si lo estás.
          Una mochila demasiado pesada te agotará rápidamente.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Backpack Types -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-[--color-text-primary]">Tipos de mochilas</h2>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          {backpackTypes.map((type) => (
            <div class="card p-6">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center bg-[--color-bg-tertiary] rounded-lg flex-shrink-0">
                  <Icon name={type.icon as any} size={28} class="text-[--color-accent-primary]" />
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-[--color-text-primary]">{type.name}</h3>
                    <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-[--color-bg-tertiary] text-[--color-text-muted] rounded">
                      {type.capacity}
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-[--color-text-secondary] mb-3">{type.description}</p>

                  <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
                    <div>
                      <span class="text-green-400 font-medium flex items-center gap-1">
                        <Icon name="CircleCheck" size={14} />
                        Pros
                      </span>
                      <ul class="mt-1 space-y-1 text-[--color-text-muted]">
                        {type.pros.map((pro) => <li>• {pro}</li>)}
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="text-red-400 font-medium flex items-center gap-1">
                        <Icon name="CircleX" size={14} />
                        Contras
                      </span>
                      <ul class="mt-1 space-y-1 text-[--color-text-muted]">
                        {type.cons.map((con) => <li>• {con}</li>)}
                      </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="text-[--color-accent-primary] font-medium flex items-center gap-1">
                        <Icon name="Star" size={14} />
                        Ideal para
                      </span>
                      <p class="mt-1 text-[--color-text-muted]">{type.bestFor}</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Key Features -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-[--color-text-primary]">Características a buscar</h2>

        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
          {keyFeatures.map((feature) => (
            <div class="card p-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center bg-[--color-bg-tertiary] rounded-lg mb-2">
                <Icon name={feature.icon as any} size={22} class="text-[--color-accent-primary]" />
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[--color-text-primary] mb-1">{feature.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[--color-text-secondary]">{feature.description}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Recommendations -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-[--color-text-primary]">Recomendaciones por presupuesto</h2>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          {recommendations.map((rec) => (
            <div class={`card p-6 ${rec.priority === 'essential' ? 'border-l-4 border-l-red-500' : rec.priority === 'recommended' ? 'border-l-4 border-l-[--color-accent-primary]' : ''}`}>
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-3">
                <div>
                  <span class={`text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded ${rec.priority === 'essential' ? 'bg-red-500/20 text-red-400' : rec.priority === 'recommended' ? 'bg-[--color-accent-primary]/20 text-[--color-accent-primary]' : 'bg-[--color-bg-tertiary] text-[--color-text-muted]'}`}>
                    {rec.priority === 'essential' ? 'Esencial' : rec.priority === 'recommended' ? 'Recomendada' : 'Opcional'}
                  </span>
                  <span class="text-xs text-[--color-text-muted] ml-2">{rec.type}</span>
                </div>
                <span class="font-bold text-[--color-accent-primary]">{rec.price}</span>
              </div>

              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[--color-text-primary] mb-2">{rec.name}</h3>

              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
                {rec.features.map((feature) => (
                  <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-[--color-bg-tertiary] text-[--color-text-muted] rounded">
                    {feature}
                  </span>
                ))}
              </div>

              <p class="text-sm text-[--color-text-secondary] m-0">
                <strong>Veredicto:</strong> {rec.verdict}
              </p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Packing Order -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-[--color-text-primary]">Cómo cargar la mochila</h2>

        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {packingOrder.map((zone, index) => (
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4 border-b border-[--color-border] pb-4 last:border-0">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-[--color-accent-primary] text-[--color-bg-primary] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm">
                  {index + 1}
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-[--color-text-primary] mb-1">{zone.zone}</h4>
                  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-2">
                    {zone.items.map((item) => (
                      <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 bg-[--color-bg-tertiary] text-[--color-text-muted] rounded">
                        {item}
                      </span>
                    ))}
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-sm text-[--color-text-secondary] flex items-start gap-1">
                    <Icon name="Lightbulb" size={14} class="flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
                    {zone.tip}
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Kit Contents -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-[--color-text-primary]">Contenido kit 72h (ejemplo)</h2>

        <div class="card overflow-hidden">
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm">
              <thead class="bg-[--color-bg-tertiary]">
                <tr>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-4">Categoría</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-4">Artículos</th>
                  <th class="text-right py-3 px-4">Peso aprox.</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="text-[--color-text-secondary]">
                {kitContents72h.map((cat, i) => (
                  <tr class={i % 2 === 0 ? 'bg-[--color-bg-secondary]' : ''}>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 font-medium text-[--color-text-primary]">{cat.category}</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-xs">{cat.items.join(', ')}</td>
                    <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right font-mono">{cat.weight}</td>
                  </tr>
                ))}
              </tbody>
              <tfoot class="bg-[--color-bg-tertiary]">
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" class="py-3 px-4 font-bold text-[--color-text-primary]">Total aproximado</td>
                  <td class="py-3 px-4 text-right font-bold text-[--color-accent-primary]">~7.3 kg</td>
                </tr>
              </tfoot>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-[--color-bg-tertiary] text-xs text-[--color-text-muted]">
            * El agua es lo más pesado. 3L = 3kg. Considera filtro + menos agua inicial si el peso es problema.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Weight Guidelines -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-[--color-text-primary]">Guía de peso máximo</h2>

        <div class="card overflow-hidden">
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm">
              <thead class="bg-[--color-bg-tertiary]">
                <tr>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-4">Grupo</th>
                  <th class="text-center py-3 px-4">Máximo recomendado</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-3 px-4">Ejemplo</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="text-[--color-text-secondary]">
                {weightGuidelines.map((guide, i) => (
